{"tid":1042923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美女教師狎13歲男童　學生面前教室性交","createTime":"2019-03-02T01:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T03:30:19.000Z","uid":46896,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"daafbd87883b99761079ad882522a61476fb43e2","tid":1042923,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"美國亞利桑那州一名已婚女教師，去年多次與一名六年級男學生發生性行為，最終東窗事發被捕。她其後被褫奪教師資格，並被控多項猥褻兒童罪名，暫獲准以25萬美元（約195萬港元）保釋。美媒周三（2月27日）大爆女教師甚至曾在其他學生面前，在教室與男童性交。 <br />\n<br />\n案情指，28歲的扎莫拉（Brittany Zamora）於去年1月起，與男童以短訊及字條傳情，甚至交換裸照。男童供稱，扎莫拉會在課堂上假裝檢查抽屜，實際上是撫摸其下體；他其後在扎莫拉的要求下，多次於晚上離家出走，並到對方的座駕翻雲覆雨。 <br />\n<br />\n受害男童的父母發現情慾短訊後，始揭發扎莫拉惡行，於是報警並入稟法院，索償250萬美元（約1950萬港元）。扎莫拉的丈夫丹尼爾聞訊後，不僅沒有離開，反而懇求男童父母原諒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。"},{"pid":"f1d060afced6591ee6c172fa4479f74267320a3b","tid":1042923,"uid":236288,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"個口甘大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a46e00b0d625be45942cb787f2d724527f9eb67","tid":1042923,"uid":238375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:09:26.000Z","msg":"正喎"},{"pid":"d5ceb4deead343291710c3111c8f58c1efb7e806","tid":1042923,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:45:55.000Z","msg":"個男仔就爽了，又食又拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdbdddc4638ed8bf6e6a3781391fa0afd38fc76","tid":1042923,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:51:26.000Z","msg":"第一個圖load得特別慢，咩意思?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8fd0a309e8efb27169ad5b7ce7327b32c3cc1d","tid":1042923,"uid":223045,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"abdbdddc4638ed8bf6e6a3781391fa0afd38fc76","tid":1042923,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:51:26.00